        <Meaning id="449f1770-40ba-4182-9ed7-5b6d303361f0" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Sự công bằng; vốn cổ phần; giá trị tài sản ròng</Vi>
          <En>The quality of being fair and impartial; in finance, the value of shares in a company or the value of assets after debts are paid.</En>
          <Example>The company increased shareholder equity by repurchasing its own stock.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
